data.description: Check out this FULLY remodeled condo in the highly sought after Eagle Valley Farms neighborhood. You will enjoy the low maintenance lifestyle of condo living, as well as a tennis court and pool. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home has many updates, all in 2023- HVAC, water heater, flooring, rear sliding door, garage door opener, paint, kitchen cabinets, and more. Enjoy the warm days on your back deck, or the cold nights cuddled up next to your wood burning fireplace. You will be just minutes away from shopping, restaurants, and the highway.
